tihore
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a variety of farmed native flax, Phormium tenax.
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka tihori
